nodes.text: Let the Wookiee Win! is an article by Chris Prince in Star Wars Insider 121 that discusses 10 of the best Star Wars video games in the history of the franchise, going all the way back to 1983. The top 10 games in the article were Star Wars: The Arcade Game (1983), Super Star Wars: Return of the Jedi (1994), Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II (1997), Star Wars: Shadows of the Empire 1996), Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance (1999), Star Wars Episode I: Racer (1999), Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic (2003), Star Wars: Battlefront II (2004), LEGO Star Wars: The Complete Saga (2007), and Star Wars: The Force Unleashed (2008).
